Date:  18/11/1933
Source:  Press, The
Author:
Vol / Page:  15
Edition:
Quote:  Run.- ... 3. Stretch of work [shearing]. Shearers work for an hour before breakfast, two stretches in the morning and three in the afternoon. The stretches are divided by meal-times and  smokos (q.v.). (C.)
